data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-bedroom home that has been tastefully remodeled! Step into the beautiful kitchen featuring tile flooring, a stylish backsplash, stainless steel appliances, an inviting eat-in area, and updated cabinets with a pantry for all your storage needs. Enjoy the elegance of hardwood floors throughout the home. The bathroom has been completely renovated with a tile floor, a spacious vanity, and all new hardware. Fresh paint brightens up the entire home, while the newer windows let in plenty of natural light. The large, heated breezeway offers versatility as an office or playroom. Outside, the landscaped yard is mostly fenced in, complete with a fire pit and garden house. The full basement is both clean and freshly painted, providing additional space for your needs!
